OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Fovernight with clear spells.
OL,7,FTemperatures falling to give a risk of
OL,8,Ffrost. Low cloud moving into eastern
OL,9,Fparts, with areas of mist and fog
OL,10,Fdeveloping for many overnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA dry and sunny day once
OL,13,Fearly mist and fog clears. Sunshine
OL,14,Fmay be hazy at times. Warm for most,
OL,15,Fbut cooler near coasts where low cloud
OL,16,Fmay linger.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
