OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMostly
OL,6,Fdry Sunday with bright spells, then
OL,7,Frisk of heavy showers on Monday. Warm
OL,8,Fby day but patchy frost possible
OL,9,Fovernight. Drier again Tuesday but
OL,10,Fpotentially cloudy and turning cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
